Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼光芒?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從帝國首都那個方向發出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對幸運圈?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由命運改變裝置最後一次敔動\N所進行的命運改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會實現所有人的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造出絕對的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是考驗亞特蘭提斯機械\N真正價值的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯就是因為那樣才滅亡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈正在撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今主力部隊遭到殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈已經沒戲唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場勝利之後的事對我們巴斯蘭才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉向,朝北方去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在快去痛宰同盟的那群蠢豬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狄達勒斯軍,狄達勒斯軍發動偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到戰爭可能會贏,竟然馬上就來這招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要給他們好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是西薩利歐王國成為蓋亞盟主的好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊垮他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膚淺的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是少了我們,怎麼可能會打贏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著客氣給我痛宰他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍來襲,敵軍來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴斯蘭軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盟約已經蕩然無存了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在起內哄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官長,是巴斯蘭的浮遊船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞的膽小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們給我轟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低高度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游石突然飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往地面上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人應該是寨巴哈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友軍為什麼要彼此攻擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人的想法使然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追殺殘黨根本就是小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰役可還沒結束,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠實現眾人想法的,絕對幸運圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓紛爭更加擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們始終擺脫不了鬥爭的命運嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們渴望鬥爭嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然跟丟了迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡,孩子又得交給你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得要對我們的實驗內容保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死的話,我會很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭髮被他們剪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你快停下那部機器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運一旦啟動,任誰也無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若人們真的要注定毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只有認命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我找得好辛苦啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人,請您快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可以恢復成謝蕾娜…那個溫柔的謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個區區的獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把那個孩子帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把劍收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人沉迷於戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要殺了他,就能斷絕蓋亞的禍根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算殺了迪蘭度也不會因此根除人們的憤恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你豈能瞭解我的國家遭人毀滅的錐心之痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你瘋了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的罪就是我的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那全是因為她受到寨巴哈的妖術控制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量出招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一較高下吧,梵·法尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天空騎士亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會盡己所能迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝拉撒特與艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大跟國王打起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一方倒下之前,看來是不會鬆手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵跟亞連為什麼要對打?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全是他們的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的劍術真是進步神速
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真高興,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能將人型裝甲,操控得如此靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能使出如此精湛的劍技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起了巴爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要擊敗他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個年輕人還真是j喻快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的願望在絕對幸運圈實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全是因為多倫卡喀的機器在作怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多倫卡喀?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的命運持續不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去蓋亞也會跟亞特蘭提斯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我跟亞連做了了斷之後就會去殺了多倫卡喀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要再打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會結束這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去為王兄報仇,再將你給救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:11:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那種想法只會招致更多的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了保護你而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒拜託你做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不該跟亞連動手的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只會擔心亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼就是不明白我說的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明那麼為你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子明明就只想著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼就是不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯相信他\N弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的意念有時足以撼動天地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是當意念與意念重疊在一起時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒會導致巨大的隔閡產生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠將其除去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就會跟著改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔閡…意念重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意念把梵給束縛住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的在為梵著想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心信任著他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草原的氣息,梵的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡梵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒搞清楚的人原來是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認得我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都好想您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜…你終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再扔下你一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜…亞連的妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,我聽到小瞳的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終時刻終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比煉金術無法煉出黃金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運同樣是無法操控的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放棄了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信命運並不是既定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒蕪的心將引來龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨與恐懼會導致紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的龍…飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來帶我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經啟動的亞特蘭提斯機械竟然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人彼此吸引的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的意念…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:17:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌駕了背負著鬥爭命運之眾人的意念嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,善變的人心所造就出來的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有可能化為永恆嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該對我有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是你想太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒,你好壞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去占卜看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看卓也是不是真的對幸子有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很擅長算命對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻煩你幫忙算算戀愛運嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不再碰占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄,我們終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的故鄉,法尼利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你在這裏守護著國家的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得自己初次來到法尼利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是好久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你有什麼打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠大家的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來建設蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄就是希望法尼利亞\N以及蓋亞都不再依賴它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見到那樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟你一起見到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好喜歡蓋亞,好喜歡法尼利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂,如果你真想這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我們隨時都能見面不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要彼此的意念相通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著吧,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算變成了老婆婆也絕對不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉學姊真讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟天野學長好相配喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是天生一對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過得很好喔

